Package: MSI.EAGLE
Title: Interactive Mass Spectrometry Imaging Analysis and Registration Platform
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Aalim", "Weljie", , "aalimudin@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7145-4494"))
Description: MSI.EAGLE provides an interactive Shiny workflow for end-to-end
    mass spectrometry imaging (MSI) analysis, built on Cardinal and extended
    with manifold learning, clustering, phenotyping, statistics, and
    multimodal registration. It supports routine MSI workflows as well as
    optional polygon-informed single-cell mapping, spatially aware UMAP
    visualization, histology/cluster/polygon overlays, and reproducible export
    of transformed datasets and registration parameters.
